html:
Under sky full of stars
Through the satelites
Miras and Mitchell date
Ok?
When the cosmos plays
It's song of the time
A raven gets
To their nest
A nest freshly built
To grow their breed
The breed that will soon
Fly a lot
And when time comes
We will get together
Under God's approval
We'll be victorious that way
title: Miras & Mitchel
